Helen Flanagan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helen_Flanagan 0 Helen Joyce Gabriel Flanagan (born 7 August 1990) is an English actress, model, and television personality. She played the role of Rosie Webster in the ITV soap opera Coronation Street from 2000-2012 and reprised the role in 2017, before going off on maternity leave on 8 June 2018. She was voted the most attractive British celebrity in the 2013 FHM 100 Sexiest Women in the World poll.
